 />\n如果要安全的話成本高咁多<br />\n不如死多幾件罰錢算<br />\n<br />\n用鉛水管唔係罰錢<br />\n係罰你唔比投標幾個月"},{"pid":"2cb41019e8d55e0a75e960e33ea40f898ad2fa5b","tid":426980,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>裝修工程係香港都係仆街過人</blockquote><br />\n依個真，比左錢可以開一半工就唔做落去</blockquote><br />\n有冇唔係香港人做既裝修公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2723ff94198670991520dbbff25ae299a27e1ca0","tid":426980,"uid":29625,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"電訊嚟講鬼佬仲仆街過香港喎<br />\n連家居上網都限quota，仲收得好撚貴<br />\n美國佬近幾年仲想搞死埋net neutrality，好似收費電視咁限制內容收錢<br />\n香港啲電訊性價比同質素已經係世界頭幾，你識唔識㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb63a51ddd37ea0044554cb02b71198a31b9a781","tid":426980,"uid":72567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:58:11.000Z","msg":"竟然無人講食環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n專門恰9弱小社群，見到後生高挑大隻就鵪鶉咁<br />\n<br />\nDC9又係垃撚圾<br />\n黑的個啲濫收唔洗講啦，打風又坐地起價，太遠唔去太近唔去過海又唔去，我屌你老母不如唔好渣的士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81034f5fd5f02a6a30f19a98514714c38c2b2aee","tid":426980,"uid":21260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"冇撚錯 <br />\n唔想比人呃 咩都唔想買<br />\n點解咁濕鳩架"},{"pid":"fe143bdaace6d498bd13dbffcc0fe68e7487abeb","tid":426980,"uid":86988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"近排九龍灣往Megabox方向有成堆FAC乜鳩健身職員拉人入會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先叫你揀數字抽獎然後拉鳩你去間舖又問你讀書定做野又問你住邊又留電話，唔留就黑鳩你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\